  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The unborn creature nudges the eggshell with its tusks, excited to be hatched and see the universe.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">whimsical</span> nature, likely to make a playful companion.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>虽然尚未孵化，但里面的生物已经在用獠牙推挤着蛋壳，看来是已经迫不及待想要看看外面的大千世界。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">怪诞</span>的基因潜质，因此很有可能会长成一名天性爱玩的同伴。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>這隻尚未出世的生物用尖牙輕推著蛋殼，似乎等不及破殼而出探索宇宙。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">異想天開</span>的性情，可能會是個愛嬉鬧的同伴。"
  },
